## TC naming convention
Pattern: Verify that the [Module] [action] [condition]
Example: Verify that the Bookings module filter returns correct
         results when the status tab is set to Pending

## Bug severity guide
Critical: App crash, data loss, payment failure, security issue
High:     Core feature broken, incorrect data displayed to user
Medium:   Feature partially working, workaround exists
Low:      UI inconsistency, minor label or spacing issue

## Business context
Platform: Autara — service booking marketplace
User types: Admin, Merchant, Customer
Merchants create services and manage bookings
Customers discover and book merchant services
Admin oversees the full platform, approvals, reporting
Payments: Stripe Connect with KYC for merchant onboarding
Location: Google Maps for geocoding and autocomplete
Mobile: Flutter 3 apps (separate Merchant and Customer apps)
Backend: AWS AppSync GraphQL, Lambda Node.js, Cognito (3 pools)
Database: RDS PostgreSQL, Drizzle ORM
